The paper proposes a deep learning framework to enhance traditional Item Response Theory (IRT) for cognitive diagnosis in educational applications. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) as they are also related to natural language processing and deep learning. Additionally, cs.CE (Computers and Education) and cs.EDU (Education) are also likely sub-categories as the paper focuses on educational applications.
